text:
Hey, Producer.
Is it true you're making new costumes?

Yeah, I was just thinking about discussing it.
I want to schedule measurements soon...

When you decide on a date, let me know?
I'll make sure to finish it perfectly by then!

.......
What do you mean you're going to finish it...?

Of course, the body.
I mean, I'll tone up.

Ah, I see.
...But, Natsuha, you don't have to push yourself...

No, I have my own ideals.
...Well then, I'm counting on you!
